Introduction:
=============
BantamOS is a real-time premptive operating system.

Features:
=========
Tasks
Queues
Semaphores
ISR Handling

Supported Micro-Controllers:
============================
ATMega328p
ATtiny24
ATtiny44

NB:
==
Note that BantamOS is a work in progress and should probably not be
used by anybody at this point.

